summary:
Available HDT bodies: Custom CBBE/Custom UUNP/UNPB/UNP/UNPBO/7Base/7BO/CBBE Slim/Dreamgirl
She's waiting for you in the Temple of Mara, Riften.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds to your game[color=#ff00ff] [b]Francesca[/b][/color], a new follower. She's a Nord, essential, Combat Assassin, marriable, levels with the player. She's waiting for you in the [color=#ff00ff]Temple of Mara, Riften.

[url=http://imgur.com/huEhJ5P][img]http://i.imgur.com/huEhJ5P.jpg[/img][/url]
[/color]Thanks to AbsoluteAesthetics for the video he made
[youtube]ki0jrBpkSwA[/youtube]

[center][color=#ff0000][size=4][b]HDT BODY OPTIONS[/b][/size][/color][/center]
[color=#ffff00][b]Available HDT Bodies: Custom CBBE/Custom UUNP/Custom CBBE Nude/UNPB/UNP/UNPBO/7Base/7BO/CBBE Slim/Dreamgirl[/b][/color]
All bodies are HDT, so you'd better install HDT physics extensions and XPMSE skeleton to make them work properly.
Skin textures are 4k: note that UNP family options have an arm tattoo, CBBE options have not.
Now take a minute of your time, scroll down this long showcase and then choose your favourite version.
